{"tid":2402133,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"原來twitter一早比中共女間諜滲透左?","createTime":"2021-02-10T08:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T16:34:23.000Z","uid":113951,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"04d5b51a9cfc90ed079558a1ea543de2a1798cd9","tid":2402133,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:38:54.000Z","msg":"在卡迪夫大學的報告中，提及那批有組織影響美國大選的中國假用戶，有很複雜同精準的行為模式，而目的似是針對避過Twitter的言論審查演算法，有效地避過Twitter系統對可疑用戶行動的監察。簡單打個比喻，就是劫獄時有內鬼報告守衛幾時換班，閉路電視有何盲點等。<br />\n<br />\n  報告舉例了兩個例子：在這批網軍之間的不同小組，鮮有互like連結，以避免被Twitter的監察系統找出其關係而一網打盡。又識避用hashtag(只有2%的貼文有落hashtag)，以免引起Twitter注意。<br />\n<br />\n  到底Twitter是否有中共內鬼，報告似乎就不敢明言，但有暗示這批網軍如此了解Twitter的防禦機制，可能是因為有人提供機制如何運作的具體資料，於是網軍才曉得如何掩飾其行動。因為觀乎網軍對Twitter機制的了解，恐怕難以是從外部試出來。<br />\n<br />\n最可疑係呢條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n不過李飛飛在職Google期間，就請纓回流到大陸建立Google的北京人工智能實驗室，同期又爆出為Google為重返中國市場而開發加料審查搜尋器的「蜻蜓計畫」，這就很難相信李飛飛沒有牽涉在內了。<br />\n<br />\n 故此當此君一加入Twitter，大家就知她是要幫Twitter加強其言論審查演算法。而當時爆出其紅色背景的Twitter用戶，都逃不過被封鎖清洗的命運。結果Twitter在2020美國大選，在禁絕Pro Trump言論方面的確非常成功，幫深層國家將拜登推上台，又為中共除去Trump這條眼中釘。<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/601c1d1722a1137b164e7b26\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F601c1d1722a1137b164e7b26&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=60afd303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/601c1d1722a1137b164e7b26</a>"},{"pid":"c1def5579cf2b9b32d4b8c49b33db0a06765110a","tid":2402133,"uid":355943,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:41:24.000Z","msg":"一早俾人滲透左"},{"pid":"585aadfc381ac3b09020d761b8399da8a7240a12","tid":2402133,"uid":113951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c1def5579cf2b9b32d4b8c49b33db0a06765110a","tid":2402133,"uid":355943,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:41:24.000Z","msg":"一早俾人滲透左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:47:37.000Z","msg":"滲到入去到董事會級<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f54dbd8668e2c3cedd097a6dad5d2e6f2c65cdc","tid":2402133,"uid":13745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"又係中國陰道"},{"pid":"0318560fa322b93dd1fa7dbedc9d41c0413a253e","tid":2402133,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f54dbd8668e2c3cedd097a6dad5d2e6f2c65cdc","tid":2402133,"uid":13745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"又係中國陰道"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:02:07.000Z","msg":"ching chong cunts"},{"pid":"9bc66052d49f3a4c6fadb305f90a8adcd896732a","tid":2402133,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:02:40.000Z","msg":"反而係歐美左膠浸透成為一大民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nhelp me push my post please <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[堅持到底 請推上熱門] Ghosts Team告文:《魚蛋革命》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2402115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2402115</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4aea88a98872887c52073d4dff6a8600c3ff7db9","tid":2402133,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f54dbd8668e2c3cedd097a6dad5d2e6f2c65cdc","tid":2402133,"uid":13745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"又係中國陰道"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:16:10.000Z","msg":"鬼佬至愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f